#: inc/snippets/block-user-enumeration.php:17
msgid "Block user enumeration"
msgstr ""

#: inc/snippets/block-user-enumeration.php:18
msgid "Prevents the user enumeration that can be exploited by attackers to gather information about users on the WordPress site. It blocks both the default and permalink-based user enumeration URLs that reveal user IDs through author query strings, improving security."
msgstr ""

#: inc/snippets/block-user-enumeration.php:19
#: inc/snippets/disable-author-archives.php:19
#: inc/snippets/disable-pingback-trackback.php:19
#: inc/snippets/hide-wordpress-version.php:19
#: inc/snippets/protect-wp-login.php:19
msgid "Security"
msgstr ""

#: inc/snippets/clean-admin-bar.php:17
msgid "Clean up the WordPress Admin Bar"
msgstr ""

#: inc/snippets/clean-admin-bar.php:18
msgid "Removes redundant or unnecessary items from the WordPress Admin Bar, both in the backend and frontend. By cleaning up the Admin Bar, you can streamline the admin experience and improve performance."
msgstr ""

#: inc/snippets/clean-admin-bar.php:19
#: inc/snippets/clean-dashboard-items.php:19
#: inc/snippets/disable-login-language-selector.php:19
msgid "User interface"
msgstr ""

#: inc/snippets/clean-dashboard-items.php:17
msgid "Remove redundant items from the WordPress Dashboard"
msgstr ""

#: inc/snippets/clean-dashboard-items.php:18
msgid "Removes various default and plugin-related widgets from the WordPress dashboard, including the Quick Press widget, Incoming Links, and the Welcome Panel. This helps declutter the Dashboard, improving both performance and usability. The dashboard is designed to display important information about your website, not to promote advertising. I'll remove what I think is irrelevant for that purpose."
msgstr ""

#: inc/snippets/disable-adjacent-posts.php:17
msgid "Disable adjacent posts link tags in the header"
msgstr ""

#: inc/snippets/disable-adjacent-posts.php:18
msgid "Removes the rel=\"prev\" and rel=\"next\" link tags from the wp_head output, which can improve performance by reducing unnecessary HTML in the header."
msgstr ""

#: inc/snippets/disable-adjacent-posts.php:19
#: inc/snippets/disable-dashicons.php:19
#: inc/snippets/disable-dns-prefetch.php:19
#: inc/snippets/disable-emoji-scripts.php:19
